title: Red Math - War Games & Cool Out - Urban Sickness Audio (USA1007)
description:
Urban Sickness Audio: USA1007

Artist: Red Math
Title: War Games / Cool Out


Red Math lays down his first release of 2011 in the shape of dance floor smashers War Zone and Cool Out.

A hard hitting barrage of Drum & Bass and Dubstep layered with growling bass lines and dangerously heavy beats set against an ominous sci-fi vista in true Red Math style.
